CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Solon's Family - Member's of the councilman's family were, left to right, Mrs. W. Augustus Jones, the Rev. W. Augustus Jones, both of Fifth Street Baptist Church, Louisville, Ky.; his father; Mr. and Mrs. P. F. Jones, William A. Jones, brothers; Mrs. Loretta McCallister, Cincinnati; sister, and Mrs. William A. Jones."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Mrs. Jones, Rev. W. Augustus Jones, Paul F. Jones, Antoinette Jones, William A. Jones, Loretta McCallister, and Mrs. Jones, standing in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers, City County Building
